list.comment: added support for vehicle/trip resolution and missing fields in database models

task.summary: Default task
initial commit
added file information header
switched configuration to production level
optimized controller structure and added documentation
defined table relations and basic findAll selector methods
implemented basic common selector methods
improved trip/byStopId selector and trip sort by departure time
added query logger for debug mode
improved ordering of stop times and shapes loading
re-generated model files for type safety and added config file
intended ControllerDispatcher class for simplifying the invention of new controller classes
implemented basic fare support
moved global constants definition into config folder
idea fix commit
added documentation and license
adapted composer.json
several bugfixes in stop controller
response parameter name 'response' => 'result'
updated related objects to be null by default
adaption of package names
improved order of routes
bugfix in TripController - improved ordering by departure time
added CHANGELOG.md and updated information
composer support for gtfs/realtime-php and gtfs/csa-php for next updates
added basic controller support for GTFS-realtime and POST calls
generated GTFS-realtime model classes and internal relationships
basic implementation for posting GTFS-realtime alerts
implementation for posting GTFS-relatime trip updates
re-generated database models with primary key and implemented support for posting GTFS-realtime vehicle positions
implemented selector for selecting a trip by its serving vehicle ID based on realtime data
included realtime data into standard API responses, updated relationships
added support for vehicle/trip resolution and missing fields in database models
